title: Fitness His Edition Magazine - Jan Feb 2013 SA
description:
Fitness His Edition Magazine January February 2013 South Africa


Fitness His Edition magazine covers all aspects of the mens health and fitness lifestyle with dedicated weight training features that delve into everything related to gym-based training, as well as various sporting codes and related training. Fitness His Edition also covers health and fitness product news, trends and techniques, as well as expert nutritional and supplementation information from the industries top experts - all delivered in a well designed, attractive looking layout that entices readers to carry on feeding their hunger for information.

84 Pages | 93 MB | PDF | English
